{"tid":807525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[悲歌]流動廁所放彎位 女車長如廁後步出即被城巴撞","createTime":"2018-09-05T14:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T16:03:58.000Z","uid":176553,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"041e1d63239ec5228c90d790ea83ea1dbbf5e4c5","tid":807525,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536151403_e0a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536151403_e0a0.jpg&h=67883ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536151038_9830.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536151038_9830.jpg&h=4b8ba254&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣發生交通意外，傍晚6時許，一名女車長在耀東邨巴士總站的流動廁所跑出時，被一部駛至的99號線城巴撞傷。現場消息稱，女車長受傷卧地動彈不得，她事後由救護車送往東區醫院治理。據現場所見，該流動廁所設於巴士站的一個彎位上，巴士駛出站時與廁所距離僅得數呎。<br />\n<br />\n涉事99號路線城巴來往筲箕灣至海怡半島，上址為中途站。<br />\n<br />\n新巴發言人回應查詢時指，傍晚6時半，一輛99號往筲箕灣方向的城巴，駛離巴士站時撞倒一名新巴車長，事後受傷車長送院治理，公司會配合警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n個屎坑放正路中間，痾痾下屎比車撞死都唔知咩事。"},{"pid":"46ccfa47886b141d992ce771f595dafe88e3263b","tid":807525,"uid":93900,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"擺個咁既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a2ad86116fe90a3938a7964a7bacfe26503c63","tid":807525,"uid":132587,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"不如擺係路中心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e74db61a44f81d1a7aaf0d181a553bc17e4e2","tid":807525,"uid":36013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"299a04ada0f0ae9d48d46643a6f573e891433820","tid":807525,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite